emo site, follow the steps mentioned in the&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://doc.ez.=
no/doc_hidden/Extensions/Exponential-extensions/Website-Interface/Website-in=
terface-5.2-upgrade" rel=3D"nofollow">eZ Webin</a>,&nbsp;<a href=3D"https:/=
/doc.ez.no/doc_hidden/Extensions/Exponential-extensions/eZ-Flow/Upgrading-eZ=
-Flow/eZ-Flow-5.2-upgrade" rel=3D"nofollow">eZ Flow</a>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<a hre=
f=3D"https://doc.ez.no/doc_hidden/Extensions/Exponential-extensions/eZ-Demo/=
eZ-Demo-5.2-upgrade" rel=3D"nofollow">eZ Demo</a>&nbsp;upgrade documentatio=
n.</p>
